The paper deals with deep learning approaches for pose-guided resynthesis of human photographs, which involves image generation, image inpainting, and image correspondence. These topics are closely related to computer vision (cs.CV), graphics (cs.GR), multimedia (cs.MM), machine learning (cs.LG), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper, ordered from most to least likely.
